HEADWORD: Coadventure
<hw>Co`ad*ven"ture</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An
adventure in which two or more persons are partakers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coadventure</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Coadventure
<hw>Co`ad*ven"ture</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To share in a
venture.</def> <rj><au>Howell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coadventurer</ent>⟦br⟧
